if I had pierced her daughter's hymen.

11:10.086 --> 11:13.255
And I told her, "No, Rebecca showed up
to camp with those earrings."

11:14.090 --> 11:15.383
Wow.

11:15.466 --> 11:18.302
What if people don't like me?
What if I say the wrong thing?

11:18.386 --> 11:20.638
What if an old person calls me "Oriental"?

11:20.721 --> 11:21.722
[chuckles]

11:21.806 --> 11:26.018
Look, Josh, I'm a man of God and I try
to believe the best about everyone,

11:26.102 --> 11:28.896
but if you think you're gonna make it
through a whole weekend

11:28.979 --> 11:32.274
with a bunch of 70-year-olds
and not get called an "Oriental,"

11:32.358 --> 11:33.651
you're out of your ever-loving mind.

11:33.734 --> 11:35.694
-[bird twittering]
-Oh!

11:36.612 --> 11:38.739
[sighs]
Nope.

11:38.823 --> 11:41.742
Father Brah, I've been bouncing
from girl to girl all year.

11:41.826 --> 11:45.037
I've told everyone in my life,
including my followers on Moviefone,

11:45.121 --> 11:47.415
that Rebecca and I are the real deal.

11:47.498 --> 11:50.334
This relationship has to work out.
It just has to.

11:50.418 --> 11:52.962
Because it's the main thing
going on in your life right now?

11:54.046 --> 11:55.047
Yeah, kinda.

11:55.131 --> 11:59.260
Josh, do you think you're defining
yourself through your relationship?

12:00.469 --> 12:02.805
