Where are you, you little minx?

12:09.145 --> 12:11.230
Brah, I didn't know
you were into birdwatching.

12:11.313 --> 12:14.150
Oh, no, I'm not. I stashed my weed
in one of these trees.

12:14.859 --> 12:17.862
Oh! Yeah, there it is.

12:24.660 --> 12:27.163
Okay, so, if my mom asks,
you have no opinion on politics,

12:27.246 --> 12:28.914
I've been using
the bath salts she sent me,

12:28.998 --> 12:31.167
and the Garfinkel ring
is in the safe deposit box.

12:31.250 --> 12:34.628
-What's the Garfinkel ring?
-It's a long story. I'll tell you later.

12:34.712 --> 12:38.048
Okay, this is gonna be great
because, with you here, I'll be calm.

12:38.132 --> 12:41.760
-I love you.
-I love you too. It's gonna be great.

12:42.720 --> 12:44.054
Oh!

12:45.347 --> 12:47.975
