-Mom!

12:49.185 --> 12:50.269
[sighs]

12:57.610 --> 12:59.195
Would you--
Would you please put on a robe?

12:59.278 --> 13:03.365
I just moisturized. It has to soak in
for an hour or I'm wasting the La Mer.

13:03.449 --> 13:04.617
La Mer is for your face.

13:04.700 --> 13:07.495
I know it's for my face,
but, for once, I'm splurging on myself!

13:07.578 --> 13:10.915
I got you this Hollywood sign magnet
from the airport.

13:14.376 --> 13:17.046
-What's with the hair?
-Are you gonna say "thank you"?

13:17.129 --> 13:20.966
