but you look like a wet rescue dog.

13:21.050 --> 13:23.052
You know what?
Maybe we should just stay at a hotel.

13:23.135 --> 13:25.513
-We don't have to stay here.
-Oh, please. Don't be so dramatic.

13:25.638 --> 13:26.722
You came all this way

13:26.805 --> 13:30.017
