13:30.100 --> 13:33.103
And, Becky, do you know
what Torah portion they gave Skyler?

13:33.187 --> 13:34.855
-What?
-The one with the menstruation

13:34.939 --> 13:36.065
and the lepers.

13:36.148 --> 13:40.110
